data.description: This exquisite 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers not only spacious living but also a maintenance free lifestyle. Upon entering, you'll be immediately greeted by an abundance of natural light from the expansive windows, complemented by vaulted ceilings that create an airy and inviting atmosphere. For those who work from home, the french doors beckon you into a dedicated space off the living room that makes for the perfect home office. The living room is a true centerpiece of this home, featuring a beautifully redone fireplace wall that adds a touch of elegance and warmth to the space. Off the living room, you'll find a large dining room space, which will fit a table for 6 or 8. The kitchen includes granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, including a gas range that elevate your cooking experience. Leading off the kitchen is a large private deck – ideal place for your morning coffee, evening barbecues, or simple unwinding and enjoying the spectacular Colorado weather! Your personal oasis awaits in the spacious primary suite, complete with a 5-piece bathroom that exudes luxury, and a generous walk-in closet providing ample storage. Built-in speakers throughout the home ensure that your favorite tunes or podcasts are just a button press away, setting the perfect ambiance for any occasion. Additionally, a finished basement offers flexibility, providing an additional bedroom for guests and enough space to create your very own workout area. Don't miss your chance to make it your own! 2.25% FHA Assumable Rate!
